{"questionId":"17390","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Consider the differential equation&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{\\text{d}}y}}{{{\\text{d}}x}} = \\frac{{4{x^2} + {y^2} - xy}}{{{x^2}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>4</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>y</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>, with <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y = 2\">\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n</math></span> when&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x = 1\">\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Express&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"{m^2} - 2m + 4\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <mrow> <msup> <mi>m</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow> <mo>−</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mi>m</mi> <mo>+</mo> <mn>4</mn> </math></span>&nbsp;in the form&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"{\\left( {m - a} \\right)^2} + b\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <mrow> <msup> <mrow> <mo>(</mo> <mrow> <mi>m</mi> <mo>−</mo> <mi>a</mi> </mrow> <mo>)</mo> </mrow> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow> <mo>+</mo> <mi>b</mi> </math></span> , where&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"a{\\text{, }}b \\in \\mathbb{Z}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <mi>a</mi> <mrow> <mtext>,&nbsp;</mtext> </mrow> <mi>b</mi> <mo>∈</mo> <mrow> <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">Z</mi> </mrow> </math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"{m^2} - 2m + 4 = {\\left( {m - 1} \\right)^2} + 3\\,\\,\\,\\,\\,\\left( {a = 1,\\,b = 3} \\right)\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"> <mrow> <msup> <mi>m</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow> <mo>−</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mi>m</mi> <mo>+</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mo>=</mo> <mrow> <msup> <mrow> <mo>(</mo> <mrow> <mi>m</mi> <mo>−</mo> <mn>1</mn> </mrow> <mo>)</mo> </mrow> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow> <mo>+</mo> <mn>3</mn> <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace> <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace> <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace> <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace> <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace> <mrow> <mo>(</mo> <mrow> <mi>a</mi> <mo>=</mo> <mn>1</mn> <mo>,</mo> <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace> <mi>b</mi> <mo>=</mo> <mn>3</mn> </mrow> <mo>)</mo> </mrow> </math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[1 mark]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"17390","referenceCode":"19N.3.AHL.TZ0.Hca_4c.i","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Express m 2 − 2 m + 4 in the form ( m − a ) 2 + b , where a , b ∈ Z .","paper":"3","level":"HL","questionNumber":"c.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5 —Calculus","Topic 5 —Calculus","AHL 5.18—1st order DE’s – Euler method, variables separable, integrating factor, homogeneous DE using sub y=vx"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}